<div class="mb-5">

    <!-- Header with brief explanation -->
    <h1 class="text-center header-lg mb-3 d-md-block d-none">Welcome to Budget Simple</h1>
    <h1 class="text-center mb-3 d-md-none d-block">Welcome to Budget Simple</h1>
    <p class="text-center fs-5 col-12 col-md-6 offset-md-3">This page will be your dashboard. Once you set up
        your
        first budget,
        you'll find everything you need right here! </p>
